title: Sports Illustrated India - March 2016
description:
English | 92 Pages | PDF | 29.1 Mb

Sports Illustrated was first published by Time Warner in 1954 and is now read by over 23 million people every week, of which 18 million are men - that's 19% of the male population of the United States. It is the quintessential voice of sport in the USA and the magazine has won countless awards for its incisive, arresting journalism and stunning imagery
